[center][size=30pt][b][font=Times New Roman]Server Info[/font][/b][/size][/center] [center][b]Unrivaled Gods[/b] is an active and well-established Runescape Private Server. [b]Online 24/7[/b], [b]Unrivaled Gods[/b] has a friendly and dedicated community with active staff ready to help whoever is in need. It will blow your mind with its amazing skilling, economy and custom points system. Players are rewarded daily for voting and there are many donator/member benefits![/center]
[center][IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/2nb4izr.png[/img][/center]
[center][b][size=15pt][font=Times New Roman]Prestige[/font][/size][/b] [font=Arial][size=10pt][/center][center]You might be wondering: what the hell is prestige? Ight. Prestige is a rank that you can earn by maxing out all your stats. At the moment, you can prestige 30 times. Leveling up gets harder after each prestige so it'll be more interesting and more challenging. By prestiging, you get [b]Prestige Points[/b] wich can be used on our prestige shop to get yourself a little reward for all the hard work. Your drop rates are also increased everytime you prestige, so, the higher your prestige is, the better are the chances to get rare drops.[/center]

[center][b][size=15pt][font=Times New Roman]Skilling[/font][/size][/b][/center] [center][font=Arial]Each time you level up on any skill, you get [b]10 skillpoints[/b]. You can use your [b]skillpoints[/b] to buy some goodies from our skilling points shop. Skilling won't be that boring anymore since you can get alot of stuff just by leveling up [/font][/center]
[center][IMG]http://i58.tinypic.com/34t661g.png[/img][/center]
[center][font=Arial]If you prestige atleast once you will be able to access and buy whatever you want from our special prestige skilling store![/font][/center]

[center][font=Times New Roman][size=15pt][b]Annihilation Points[/b][/size][/font][/center] [center]Here, with us, [b]you'll get points by killing monsters[/b]. [b]Every monster[/b] gives a certain amount of [b]Annihilation Points[/b] wich can be used on our shops to buy some gear and lots of weapons![/center]
